ZH: 我明天要考试，所以我在复习试卷。
EN: I have an exam tomorrow, so I am reviewing my test papers.

ZH: 请把试卷交给老师。
EN: Please hand in your test papers to the teacher.

ZH: 我已经完成了所有的试卷。
EN: I have finished all the exam papers.

ZH: 这个试卷太难了，我不知道怎么做。
EN: This test paper is too difficult, I don't know how to do it.

ZH: 我很担心我会不会在试卷上丢分。
EN: I am worried that I might lose points on the test paper.

ZH: 他在考试中得了最高分，所有试卷都拿满分了。
EN: He got the highest score in the exam, he scored full marks on all the test papers.

ZH: 请大家拿出笔和试卷。
EN: Please take out your pens and test papers.

ZH: 这是我们的数学试卷，你们可以开始了。
EN: This is our math test paper, you may begin.

ZH: 我想给你一张白纸，你可以在上面写试卷。
EN: I'd like to give you a blank sheet of paper, you can write your test paper on it.

ZH: 请按照试卷上的要求填写个人信息。
EN: Please fill in your personal information according to the requirements on the test paper.

ZH: 我把答案写在试卷上了。
EN: I wrote the answers on the test paper.

ZH: 这个试卷包括多种题型，比如选择题和填空题。
EN: This test paper includes various question types, such as multiple choice and fill in the blanks.

ZH: 题目是在试卷的第三页。
EN: The questions are on the third page of the test paper.

ZH: 别忘了在试卷上写上你的姓名和日期。
EN: Don't forget to write your name and date on the test paper.

ZH: 请仔细阅读试卷上的每个题目。
EN: Please read each question on the test paper carefully.

ZH: 这个试卷的难度适中。
EN: The difficulty level of this test paper is moderate.

ZH: 她得了满分，因为她在试卷上回答得非常准确。
EN: She scored full marks because she answered the test paper very accurately.

ZH: 我的试卷上有一道题没有回答，我忘记了。
EN: There is one question on my test paper that I didn't answer, I forgot.

ZH: 请务必把试卷在规定的时间内交给我。
EN: Please make sure to hand in your test papers to me within the designated time.

ZH: 这堂考试的试卷比较简单。
EN: The test paper for this exam is relatively easy.
